<TITLE>Pre-Flight SIR-C Education CD-ROM</TITLE>
<H1>Pre-Flight SIR-C Education CD-ROM</H1>
<HR>
<P>The pre-flight CD-ROM is available <A
HREF="http://ericir.syr.edu/NASA/nasa.html">online </A>, 
or you may request your own <a href="sirced_update.html">copy </a>.  
<A HREF="infosirced.html">General information about the CD-ROM may be
found here</A>.
The on-line version was put together by Dave Lankes , and resides at the AskERIC
site, Syracuse University.</p>
