<DOCHDR>
http://southport.jpl.nasa.gov:80/sampledata/Readme.dataformat.html 137.78.28.58 19970208202913 text/html 14892
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netsite-Communications/1.0
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 20:30:23 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 01-Nov-94 22:01:14 GMT
Content-length: 14701
