<TITLE>Software Manuals</TITLE>
<H1>Software Manuals</H1>
<HR>
<p>Software users guides and manuals are listed below.  This software is
provided to facilitate analysis of <a href="radardata.html">SIR-C data</a>. 
For those
interested in analyzing radar data, <a
href="software/license.html">software licenses</a> for <a href="obtainsoft.html">
obtaining
the software</a> are provided. Unfortunately, the software is not yet available on
line.  Some software is also available through <a
href="cosmic.html">COSMIC</a>.
<hr>
<p>Unfortunately, some of this software has changed since these manuals
were written, and we have not had time to update the manuals. For the
first time user, I recommend looking at the <a
href="software/demo/demo.html">UNIX Step by Step cookbook
approach to viewing your first image.</a></p>
<hr>
<UL>
<li><a href="software/db-byte/db-byte_ToC.html">db-byte software
manual</a></li>
<p>
<lI><A HREF="software/cr/cr.html">CEOS_READER software manual</a></li>
<P></P>
