<title>Spaceborne Synthetic Aperture Radar : Current Status and Future
Directions</title>
<p></p>
<p> NASA Technical Memorandum 4679</p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<h1>Spaceborne Synthetic Aperture Radar : Current Status and Future
Directions</h1>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
