science community, Caltech/JPL is distributing the Software and Related Materials to the radar 
science community on a non-royalty, nonexclusive basis, subject to similar terms as this license 
as applicable.  The SIR-C program now has 500 Principal Investigators collaborating with them 
on image radar activity.  This  license is intended to support that effort.  It is understood that this 
license is concurrent and consistent with COSMIC's license to distribute the Software.
     
