<p>
<b>Volume Directory File:</b><p>
<b>
<a name="RTFToC11">Text
Record:
</a></b><p>
<b></b><p>
The purpose of this record is to allow the reader of the CEOS tape to simply
print out a short description of the data <p>
<p>
<b>Field	Bytes	Format	Source	Parameter	Description</b><p>
<b></b><p>
1	1-4	B4	RDC	---	Record sequence number<p>
2	5	B1	RDC	---	1st record subtype code (18)<p>
3	6	B1	RDC	---	Record type code (63)<p>
4	7	B1	RDC	---	2nd record subtype code (18)<p>
5	8	B1	RDC	---	3rd record subtype code (18)<p>
6	9-12	B4	RDC	---	Record length (360)<p>
7	13-14	A2	RDC	---	ASCII flag ("A$")<p>
8	15-16	A2	---	---	Continuation flag ("$$") for "not continued"<p>
9	17-56	A40	PF/RDC	pdata_product<p>
				pspecial_product	<p>
					Product type specifier ("MULTI-LOOK DETETCTED",etc.)<p>
10	57-116	A60	RDC	---	Location, date/time of CEOS product creation ("PRODUCED
AT JPL/NASA/USA ON 1994/01/16 11:45:00"<p>
11	117-156	A40	RDC	---	Physical volumes identification
("TAPE$ID:$xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx,$TAPE$1$OF$1") where xxx...x is the tape ID<p>
12	157-196	A40	PF/RDC	pdatatake_id	Site identification ("DTxxx.yy$YYYY/MM/DD
hh:mm:ss.ttt") where xxx.yy is the datatake ID and YY::tt - frame center,
acquisition date and time<p>
