25	205-208	A4	---	---	Padding for word boundary<p>
<p>
RADIOMETRIC COMPENSATION TABLE<p>
<p>
26	209-224	F16.7	OPS	---	1st compensation sample index (increment by 1)<p>
27	225-240	F16.7	RCF	---	1st compensation sample value (linear scale)<p>
<p>
Repeat fields 26-27 for each sample value in the Radiometric Compensation
File.<p>
Repeat fields 11-27+ for each data set.  (SIR-C has only one data set per
record.)<p>
