<b>
<a name="RTFToC27">File
Descriptor Record -Fixed Segment Contents
</a></b><p>
<b></b><p>
<b>Field	Bytes	Format	Source	Parameter	Description</b><p>
<b></b><p>
1	1-4	B4	OPS	---	Record sequence number (1)<p>
2	5	B1	OPS	---	1st record subtype code (63)<p>
3	6	B1	OPS	---	Record type code (192)<p>
4	7	B1	OPS	---	2nd record subtype code (18)<p>
5	8	B1	OPS	---	3rd record subtype code (18)<p>
6	9-12	B4	OPS	---	Length of this record (variable)<p>
